; Stock Trading Beancount File
; Testing cost basis with {cost} syntax

2014-01-01 open Assets:ETrade IVV
2014-01-01 open Assets:ETrade:Cash USD
2014-01-01 open Income:ETrade:CapitalGains
2014-01-01 open Expenses:Commissions

; Buy 10 shares of S&P 500 at $183.07 per share
2014-02-11 * "Bought shares of S&P 500"
  Assets:ETrade:IVV  10 IVV {183.07 USD}
  Assets:ETrade:Cash  -1830.70 USD

; Buy additional 15 shares at different price
2014-03-22 * "Bought more S&P 500"
  Assets:ETrade:IVV  15 IVV {187.12 USD}
  Assets:ETrade:Cash  -2806.80 USD

; Sell shares with explicit cost - 10 shares from first lot
2014-05-01 * "Sold shares of S&P 500"
  Assets:ETrade:IVV  -10 IVV {183.07 USD}
  Assets:ETrade:Cash  1979.00 USD
  Income:ETrade:CapitalGains  -148.30 USD

; Sell shares using date match
2014-05-15 * "Sold by date"
  Assets:ETrade:IVV  -15 IVV {2014-03-22}
  Assets:ETrade:Cash  2925.00 USD
  Income:ETrade:CapitalGains  -118.20 USD

; Buy with reference label
2014-06-01 * "Bought with ref"
  Assets:ETrade:IVV  20 IVV {190.00 USD, "ref-001"}
  Assets:ETrade:Cash  -3800.00 USD

; Sell using reference label
2014-06-15 * "Sold by reference"
  Assets:ETrade:IVV  -20 IVV {"ref-001"}
  Assets:ETrade:Cash  4000.00 USD
  Income:ETrade:CapitalGains  -200.00 USD

; Cost with price for generating price entry
2014-07-11 * "Sold with price entry"
  Assets:ETrade:IVV  -10 IVV {183.07 USD} @ 197.90 USD
  Assets:ETrade:Cash  1979.00 USD
  Income:ETrade:CapitalGains  -148.30 USD